"Dont know if anyone needs this, but here is how to start Valorant from another Launcher:

In this example i will use Steam, but it should work more or less the same on other launchers which have these options:

Adding games from other sources

Adding launch parameters

# Adding the Game

Click on ""Add a Game"" on the bottom left in your Library on Steam

Click on ""Add a Non-Steam Game""

In the opened window, click on the ""Browse"" button

Navigate to ""C:/Riot Games/Riot Client""

Select RiotClientServices.exe

Click ""Add Selected Programs"" in the Steam Window

# Configuration

Search for RiotClientServices in your Library and select it.

Click on the gear icon under the bottom right of the game banner.

Click on ""Properties""

