Intensive Aim Development (Post-Session Training)
In contrast to the warm-up, skill-development training is often conducted after the day's primary gaming session to prevent performance degradation during competitive matches.The current standard involves specialized routines in software like Kovaak’s or Aimlabs, focusing on micro-adjustments and target acquisition speed.

