Iron
Very little crosshair discipline (aiming at the floor/walls instead of head height)

Gun mechanics (not knowing when to burst, tap, spray etc).

Tunnel vision on shooting instead of positioning and/or moving.

Bronze
Utility dumped early with no follow-up (they think just using util in general automatically has value, so often is just completely misused. contrary to the middle-ranks who actually die without even using it which will be mentioned later)

Chasing kills while ignoring the objective

Silver
Inconsistent decision-making (good aim one round, tunnel vision on flashy plays)

Fighting without information or team presence

Gold
